productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Montserrat has one of these. She works as a circus performer and she says it looks shriveled.
My neighbor Elisha has one of these. She works as a fortune teller and she says it looks floppy.
I saw one of these in Libya and I bought one.
The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 light-year and weights 15 gram!!!
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
